title: Thought on Snapshot
body: We now have off chain snapshot voting support available. I think this will be a great use case for the Community to get involved where we can vote on those public proposals within our Organization's DAO (https://app.daohaus.club/dao/0x89/0xc48996a569911fd6eba1b97b6419731eed32041e/).
author: 0x1Fde40a4046Eda0cA0539Dd6c77ABF8933B94260
